Class VoteBoxBoothView

    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class VoteBoxBoothView
extends AMachineView
    The view of a VoteBox booth on the network. Shows information such as the label, status, battery level, and public/protected counts. It also has a button for authorization or override. The button is hidden when the polls are closed.
